lastCommitMessage: feat: enhance localization for admin features
- Updated the admin dashboard and product editor pages to utilize localized strings for various management features, improving accessibility for English and Traditional Chinese users.
- Added new localization entries for admin-related actions and messages, ensuring a consistent user experience across the admin interface.
- Enhanced error handling and user feedback in the orders tab and shipping info dialog, contributing to a more user-friendly interface for managing orders and shipping details.
These changes improve the overall usability and inclusivity of the admin features.
